Mr Pietro Carlomagno has been registered since 2004 in the Registry of Qualified Accountants and Bookkeepers of Milan (in Italian Albo dei Dottori Commercialisti e degli Esperti Contabili di Milano) and he has joined the Funding and Calls Commission of Accountants and Bookkeepers of Milan on May 2018. His working experience is focused on financial, tax, accounting, legal and audit of small and medium-large enterprises, with a qualification in contexts connected to service and  financial sector (lending institution, Bank of Italy regulations - Uif).&#xd;
